name: アイリス - Iris Pokemon
description:
A LoRA of Iris from Pokémon. Trained on NAI.

HOW TO SWAP BETWEEN HER 3 STYLES

Pokemon Black/White style : put Iris A in the positives, and "IrisB, IrisC" in the Negatives.

Pokemon Black 2/White 2 style : put IrisB in the positives, and "IrisA, IrisC" in the negatives.

Pokemon Masters alternative outfit : Put IrisC in the positives, and "IrisA, IrisB" in the negatives. Not perfect.

(put a lot of weight in the negatives to get better results)

See samples for good prompts for each style too.

If you like this LoRA, please reviews it!

All of my LoRAs will always be free. If you paid for this or an image using this LoRA, you got scamed! If you wants to supports me, feel free to buy me a Ko-Fi.
